    {
      "id": "37",
      "name": "Properties",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tutorial",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage 1",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "In Stage 1, Shouki no Kami will perform large AoE attacks using different elements. At the same time, Energy Blocks will appear.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/fa7a89afe75a703849097380b3bba0c6_5396866780563694673.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "In addition, there are different types of Elemental Matrices in the arena.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Pick up the Energy Blocks generated during the battle to charge the Neo Akasha Terminal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the Neo Akasha Terminal is fully charged, Travelers can move towards the Elemenatal Matrix and use the Neo Akasha Terminal button to activate the effect of the corresponding matrix.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The effects of the Elemental Matrices are as follows:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "-",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Pyro",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ": Clears the Raw Frost effect from the ground.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "-",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(153, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Cryo",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ": Clears the Remnant Flame effect from the ground.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "-",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(128, 255, 215)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Anemo",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ": Creates an Upcurrent with which you can dodge some of Shouki no Kami's attacks.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "-",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(128, 192, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Hydro",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ": Creates a continuous healing effect.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "-",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Electro",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ": Suppresses Shouki no Kami. Activate it again while a suppression effect is active to overload and paralyze him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/63c1f7ce65a1da43192719eed3579402_2292378566674930044.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*Using the Elemental Matrices strategically may make your fight easier!",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/980729c3b8a376341f977450afcec78d_1659231130655048693.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage 2",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "At the beginning of Stage 2, Shouki no Kami will be protected by a shield, which greatly increases his RES.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/fd1dd3f4770d8a120fa5ae84e7c5508d_4006952947897005544.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "After Shouki no Kami unleashes an attack, Energy Blocks will appear.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/b93ae33c7b77785a7b41c9c403df618d_1254607635596514517.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Pick up the Energy Blocks and fully charge the Neo Akasha Terminal to hit Shouki no Kami with a more powerful aimed attack which will weaken his shield.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*When energy is fully charged, use the Neo Akasha Terminal button and hold the button to aim its attack.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*Using Elemental Reactions to destroy the entities summoned by Shouki no Kami or directly attack Shouki no Kami will also replenish energy for the Neo Akasha Terminal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/b28435807a9e2b133e295f036a0a1390_5569045565389607354.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/10/35428890/8cfad94d9240966a5559462f672677c4_7053910199481662706.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "When his shield is destroyed for the first time, Shouki no Kami will begin charging up energy to unleash Setsuna Shoumetsu and summon a Nirvana Engine at the same time.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/9e6ed13c7acbdb167a1fca2cf1a09a4d_1113074260436659221.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/19fff3e6254a05c1d2ce85344ea8ca10_9172111063519384691.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "During this period, use Elemental Reactions to destroy the Nirvana Engine to generate Energy Blocks and charge the Neo Akasha Terminal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/bc4594d7e8d0121510c45ee3ad0f7c49_3897638574451900675.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Once fully charged, use the Neo Akasha Terminal to aim and attack Shouki no Kami, which will topple him over and immobilize him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/66c6dedf5352ac48f6288d0db4f2de63_8056870910893381205.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "•",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Make use of the Four-Leaf Sigils to quickly move to the platform in front of Shouki no Kami and directly attack his body to deal damage more effectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/35428890/4c87f4de9a95ffcc190b24b83755c585_8215691764785161986.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Achievements",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
